      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "魔法少女とサキュバスに振り回される主人公の\nお話……！？　す、すっごくエッチじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A story about a protagonist pushed around\nby a magical girl and succubi…!? T-That sounds so lewd!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.5333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.0483694712
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～……SFやミステリーもあるんですね\nどれも面白そう……私達が選ばれるといいなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh wow… there's SF and mystery options too.\nThey all look interesting… I hope our group gets chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5666687012,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 318.2992300999956,
          "startTime": 90.3666687013
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ここに書いてある五つの企画の中から\nファン投票で一つ選んでもらうんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Out of these five proposals listed here‚\nthe fans will vote to pick one‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.215030543
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。投票結果を見てからのお楽しみだな\nそれまでは選ばれるようにアピールしていかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. We'll have to wait for the results to find out.\nUntil then‚ we need to promote it so we get chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.2414930343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
