      "text": "そうですね！　今度ラジオのお仕事があるので\nそこでファンに呼びかけてみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right! I have a radio job coming up‚\nso I'll try calling out to the fans there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1666631063,
      "sfxList": []
