    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん！\n投票の結果ってもう出ましたか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work today‚ {user}!\nHave the voting results come out yet!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、決まったよ。今回選ばれたテーマは……\n『どきドキ♡ラブコメファンタジー』だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's settled. The chosen theme is…\n\"Doki Doki♡ Rom-com Fantasy.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.0881636937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "ホントですか！？　やったー！\nいろんな所でアピールした甲斐がありました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? Yay—!\nMy efforts to promote it everywhere paid off!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "登場人物はもう決まっているから\n配役はすみれ達で自由に決めていいと言っていたぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The characters are already set‚\nso they said you all can decide the roles freely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3714969518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
