      "text": "すみれ、落ち着いてくれ。まだサキュバスをやると\n決まった訳じゃないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down‚ Sumire. It's not like it's decided\nthat you're playing the succubus yet.",
        "id": ""
