      "text": "そ、そうですよね……今度みんなで集まって\n話し合いをしながら決めようと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Right… We're planning to meet up soon\nand decide together through discussion!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.733329773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
