      "text": "渚さんが使い魔で、千紗さんと瑠依ちゃんが\nサキュバス、そして……私が魔法少女になりました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-san is the familiar‚ and Chisa-san and Rui-chan\nare the succubi‚ and… I'm the magical girl!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.6143806226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.8848402659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
