      "text": "おお、早速決めてくれたんだな\nみんな、なりたい役にはなれたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you decided quickly.\nDid everyone get the role they wanted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.0666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 207.7054750442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
