      "text": "それが、壮絶な役の奪い合いになって……！\n話し合いで決まらなかったので、くじ引きで決めました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ it was a fierce battle for the roles…!\nWe couldn't agree‚ so we decided by drawing lots.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.733329773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
