      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "あまり気負い過ぎないようにな\nすみれらしい姿をファンは観たいだろうから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't put too much pressure on yourself.\nThe fans want to see the Sumire they know.",
